OL,3,CKate completes Three Peaks challenge
OL,4,Cto 'explore life beyond' cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FThe Princess of Wales has released a
OL,8,Fphoto from the top of Ben Nevis,
OL,9,Fmarking the completion of her Three
OL,10,FPeaks Challenge to raise money for a
OL,11,Fcancer charity and "explore life
OL,12,Fbeyond diagnosis".
OL,14,FKate revealed in a message on social
OL,15,Fmedia that she had successfully taken
OL,16,Fon the trek, not only as a physical
OL,17,Fendeavour but "to give something back"
OL,18,Fand raise awareness of the wider
OL,19,Fimpact of serious illness.
OL,26,@yD@OOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
