PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782733686
OL,3,CKate completes Three Peaks challenge
OL,4,Cto 'explore life beyond' cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FThe future queen climbed the highest
OL,8,Fmountains in Scotland, England and
OL,9,FWales ` Ben Nevis, Scafell Pike and
OL,10,FSnowdon ` within 24 hours this
OL,11,Fweekend, starting on Saturday evening.
OL,13,FShe carried out the challenge solo,
OL,14,Fsupported on route by Mountain Rescue,
OL,15,Fand was greeted at the end by the
OL,16,FPrince of Wales and her children,
OL,17,FPrince George, Princess Charlotte and
OL,18,FPrince Louis, and her parents Carole
OL,19,Fand Michael Middleton and brother
OL,20,FJames Middleton.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782733686
OL,3,CKate completes Three Peaks challenge
OL,4,Cto 'explore life beyond' cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"I have taken on the National Three
OL,8,FPeaks Challenge, not simply as a
OL,9,Fphysical endeavour but as a chance to
OL,10,Fexplore life beyond diagnosis and to
OL,11,Fgive something back," Kate wrote in a
OL,12,Fsocial post on Sunday.
OL,14,F"The Royal Marsden is a place that
OL,15,Fholds great meaning for me and whose
OL,16,Fcare and expertise are life-changing
OL,17,Ffor so many people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782733686
OL,3,CKate completes Three Peaks challenge
OL,4,Cto 'explore life beyond' cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"Through this challenge, I want to
OL,8,Fraise awareness for the deeper impact
OL,9,Fof serious illness and the importance
OL,10,Fof holistic healthcare."
OL,12,FThe princess has recently returned to
OL,13,Fpublic-facing engagements following
OL,14,Fcancer treatment at the Royal Marsden
OL,15,FHospital in 2025 for an undisclosed
OL,16,Fform of the disease.
OL,18,FShe is now in remission after
OL,19,Fundergoing chemotherapy following her
OL,20,Fdiagnosis the previous year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
