OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782733686
OL,3,CKate completes Three Peaks challenge
OL,4,Cto 'explore life beyond' cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FThe princess wrote: "Every year,
OL,8,Fhundreds of thousands of people in
OL,9,Fthis country hear the words no one
OL,10,Fwants to hear. What follows is a path
OL,11,Fthat tests every part of who we are:
OL,12,Fphysically, emotionally,
OL,13,Fpsychologically and spiritually. The
OL,14,Fchallenges ripple outwards, touching
OL,15,Ffamilies, friendships, work and the
OL,16,Fquiet moments we spend alone with our
OL,17,Fthoughts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782733686
OL,3,CKate completes Three Peaks challenge
OL,4,Cto 'explore life beyond' cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"Cancer doesn't just affect the body.
OL,8,FIt changes how you think and feel and
OL,9,Fprofoundly affects every aspect of
OL,10,Flife. I know this personally, and that
OL,11,Fthe journey through and beyond
OL,12,Ftreatment requires more than medicine
OL,13,Falone."
OL,15,FKate trekked for 23 miles, with a
OL,16,Ftotal ascent of more than 10,000 feet,
OL,17,Fand a driving distance of 462 miles
OL,18,Fbetween locations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
