PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782733686
OL,3,CKate completes Three Peaks challenge
OL,4,Cto 'explore life beyond' cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FShe was treated for cancer at the
OL,8,FRoyal Marsden Hospital in Chelsea,
OL,9,Fwest London, and The Royal Marsden
OL,10,FCancer Charity has launched a
OL,11,Fspecially designed fundraising page
OL,12,Ffor people across the nation to donate.
OL,14,FMoney raised will be used to help more
OL,15,Fpeople with cancer benefit from
OL,16,Fholistic care.
OL,18,FThe princess, who has long campaigned
OL,19,Fover the importance of spending time
OL,20,Foutdoors, wrote: "In the end, bravery
OL,21,Fisn't just about pushing forward.
OL,26,@|D@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
