OL,3,CKate completes Three Peaks challenge
OL,4,Cto 'explore life beyond' cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FKate, who signed her personal message
OL,13,Fwith a "C", also wrote of the benefit
OL,14,Fof holistic therapies, adding: "We
OL,15,Fhave an opportunity to reshape what
OL,16,Fthe future of holistic cancer care
OL,17,Flooks like, enabling more people,
OL,18,Fnationwide, to access the kind of
OL,19,Fpersonalised support that can help
OL,20,Fmake a meaningful difference during
OL,21,Fand after medical treatment."
OL,26,@uD@HOUuD@JO]vD@`OU}D@]O]
