OL,3,CKate completes Three Peaks challenge
OL,4,Cto 'explore life beyond' cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FMoney raised will also support
OL,8,Fresearch into how holistic care can
OL,9,Fbest work alongside clinical cancer
OL,10,Ftreatments to help patients, with the
OL,11,Fgoal of creating a blueprint for
OL,12,Fchange, so the supportive care becomes
OL,13,Fa standard part of cancer treatment
OL,14,Fnationally.
OL,16,FThe fundraising link is available here.
